# 🐍 Python Learning

A structured Python learning repository covering Core Python fundamentals and Advanced Python (OOP) concepts — complete with topic-wise notes, examples, and hands-on practice files.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
python-learning/
├── corepython/              # Core Python concepts & practice
│   ├── practice/            # Practice exercises
│   └── Question Bank Part-1.txt
├── advancepython/           # Advanced Python (OOP-focused)
│   ├── inheretance/         # Inheritance types
│   ├── practice2/           # Advanced practice exercises
│   └── practice_def/        # Module & package practice
├── 1weekAdvancedPython/     # Condensed 1-week advanced review
└── Advanced Python - Copy (2)/  # Extended advanced reference
```

---

