| File | Topic |
|------|-------|
| `00Variables.py` | Variables & naming rules |
| `01_datatypes.py` | Data types (int, str, list, dict, tuple, set) |
| `4 TypeCasting.py` | Type conversion |
| `5 Operators.py` | Operators (arithmetic, logical, comparison) |
| `5 If_Else.py` | Conditional statements |
| `6 loops.py` | for & while loops |
| `7 patterns.py` | Pattern printing |
| `8 comprehension.py` | List, dict & set comprehensions |
| `9 functions.py` | Functions (basics) |
| `09_00_functions.py` to `09_04_arbitrary_arg.py` | Function argument types |
| `10 recursion.py` | Recursion |
| `11 lambda.py` | Lambda functions |
| `12 map.py` | `map()` |
| `13 filter.py` | `filter()` |
| `14 reduce.py` | `functools.reduce()` |
| `15 built_in_functions.py` | Built-in functions |
| `16 return_statement.py` | Return values |
| `17 sortvsSorted.py` | `sort()` vs `sorted()` |

